Requirements
------------

DiSiCal development is done using the following fine OSS:

	postgresql 7.1.3 (jdbc drivers included in disical src)
	castor 0.9.3 (jars included in disical src)
		- requires JDK API: jta 1.0.1 
		  (included in disical src)
		- requires JDK API: jdbc-se 2.0 
		  (included in disical src)
	ORBacus ?.?
	Apache jakarta ant 1.4.1


Jakarta, ORBacus and postgresql versions used by the disical developers can be
found at ftp://ftp.berlios.de/pub/disical/tools.

Notes on Cygwin
---------------

To use postgresl under Cygwin, IPC for cygwin is required.  It is
not contained in the standard cygwin distribution, but can be
found at:

http://www.neuro.gatech.edu/users/cwilson/cygutils/V1.1/cygipc/ 


or at the disical ftp site ftp://ftp.berlios.de/pub/disical.
